parameters.name: END_TIME
parameters.description:
Stop time column. This field contains time in PDS format
    yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm:ss.sssZ. The individual elements of the
    time field can be read using the format (i4,4(1x,i2),1x,f6.3) yr,
    mon, day, hr, min, sec.

parameters.name: CHANNEL
parameters.description:
Column contains name of Low Energy Charged Particle (LECP)
    channel used to acquire this data.
